Dorothy Peterson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Peterson 0 Bergetta "Dorothy" Peterson (December 25, 1897 – October 3, 1979) was an American actress. She began her acting career on Broadway before appearing in more than eighty Hollywood films. Bergetta_"_Dorothy_"_Peterson ( December_25_,_1897 – October_3_,_1979 ) was an_American_actress .
